sequenceDiagram
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines<br/>ml-pipeline-api-server
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC/HTTP2
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432 TCP

    Note over KFP,DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Metadata Recording

    KFP->>MLMD: PutExecutionType(request)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS<br/>Optional mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE execution_type<br/>MySQL/PostgreSQL Protocol<br/>Optional TLS, Username/Password
    DB-->>MLMD: Query Result
    MLMD-->>KFP: PutExecutionTypeResponse

    KFP->>MLMD: PutExecution(execution, artifacts, events, contexts)<br/>Atomic upsert with lineage
    MLMD->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION<br/>INSERT execution, artifacts, events
    DB-->>MLMD: Commit OK
    MLMD-->>KFP: PutExecutionResponse(execution_id, artifact_ids)

    KFP->>MLMD: PutArtifacts(artifacts)<br/>Record pipeline artifacts
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE artifacts
    DB-->>MLMD: Query Result
    MLMD-->>KFP: PutArtifactsResponse(artifact_ids)

    Note over KFP,DB: Flow 2: Lineage Query

    participant Client as Pipeline UI / Client

    Client->>MLMD: GetLineageSubgraph(query)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS<br/>Optional mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT with graph traversal<br/>Direction, hops, boundary conditions
    DB-->>MLMD: Lineage nodes and edges
    MLMD-->>Client: LineageSubgraph(artifacts, executions, contexts, events)

    Client->>MLMD: GetArtifactsByContext(context_id)<br/>Query artifacts in a pipeline run
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT artifacts JOIN attributions
    DB-->>MLMD: Artifact records
    MLMD-->>Client: GetArtifactsByContextResponse(artifacts)
